{"tid":2188224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共國新版高中歷史書上，文革被重新定性為「內亂」","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T07:14:11.000Z","uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"323574562012dcd9c9e9fd11a73674ff6d3dd9c9","tid":2188224,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"8月30號開學後，有人發現新發嘅高一歷史課本同之前嘅課本有所唔同。<br />\n<br />\n喺文革定性部分，增加了38個字：「係一場由領導者錯誤發動，被反革命集團利用，畀黨、國家同各族人民帶嚟嚴重災難嘅內亂」。<br />\n<br />\n之前嘅課本對文革嘅定性係咁表述<br />\n「實踐證明，『文化大革命』唔係任何意義上嘅革命或社會進步。」<br />\n<br />\n到此戛然而止，冇稱其係「內亂」。"},{"pid":"080a25f5f6d78a39180d10806541ac494c1cb72b","tid":2188224,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31SCVOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31SCVOw.png&h=3280bc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJggrVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJggrVc.jpg&h=b3c9aa81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2e0AHty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2e0AHty.jpg&h=9c08f291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c68cf46943e7f6404e317a63afa3faa46b0e9898","tid":2188224,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"文革領導人係邊個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0cb46635fb6c44c3d5f0fcbc1989671ec63cd5","tid":2188224,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3a4acc58c325c34c4e7e8023d88b66a13b05b08","tid":2188224,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xRvpAQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxRvpAQw.png&h=1f52444a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b98326c59d32759ea6513d5